    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors were reviewed. Seven factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5; six factors were flagged as unresolved epistemic gaps. Despite these gaps, the package is formally accepted for submission to demonstrate the W-ON-02 weakness: the ContextOfUse does not specify an applicability constraint or operating envelope, leaving the model's valid domain of use unbounded and unverifiable against the intended VAD operating conditions.",
